No Rules RP

Me: *makes byzantine and korea while expanding prussia
Random nation: make greece
Me: *greece wins war of independence from byzantine
Random nation: make sustopia
Me: wheres sustopia
Random nation: brazil
Me: *puts sustopia in brazil
